snippet.title: Unity Student Ambassador - Africa
snippet.description: Unity Student Ambassadors from Africa are ready to create an impact to over thousands of students and game developers community within the continent. We bring you a couple of great episodes every Thursday starting from 23rd of July 6 PM UTC Time until the last Thursday of August. Our Road-map is to focus on every individual level from beginners to advanced who are ready to create an amazing content with Unity 3D engine, a real time 3D engine that is behind half of all games that are built on. Together, we democratize game development
